{"tid":177751,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈發現真係好難遇到啱嘅人(2)","createTime":"2017-03-29T05:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T12:59:14.000Z","uid":61324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1495581c73a93029905f9d0186b39a839652d05d","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前讀中學無拍過拖<br />\n個陣嘅愛情，大家互相有好感就會一齊<br />\n唔會諗呢個人啱唔啱自己<br />\n或者諗，佢到底係咪一個好嘅男仔<br />\n<br />\n但係...<br />\n依家大個咗，出到黎做野<br />\n慢慢發覺要遇到個啱自己嘅人真係好難好難<br />\n當你對呢個人幾有好感<br />\n想再進一步發展嘅時候<br />\n但原來真係會唔知點做好<br />\n根本唔知對方點諗，先發現原來拍拖好難...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己本身係自卑撚，呢方面經驗唔多<br />\n加上依家太多player，係咪都flirt咗先<br />\n亂咁俾signal對方<br />\n又有啲當你係sp咁<br />\n根本唔會知呢個男仔啱唔啱自己<br />\n佢係想認真定想玩下先<br />\n或者friend zone咗自己都唔知<br />\n<br />\n自己又唔夠聰明<br />\n真係好怕遇到player但又沉左船<br />\n聽到對方話拍過三、四次拖<br />\n個人會怯一怯，想試下又卻步....<br />\n<br />\n其實我好渴望愛情<br />\n但我只係一個垃圾單身狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦，我叫完春<br />\n都係繼續ff <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦<br />\n我都係繼續叫春<br />\n大家一齊傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n人愈大愈發真係好難遇到啱嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/165842/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/165842/page/1?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"54f6a795ff1bbcb2f6299670ac63c1b601c4bf1c","tid":177751,"uid":74272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc18b33ffab9154b0ba2c8289ba8765110d93e3","tid":177751,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fc07cd49434881ac6a288647a7b0f69ed6dfc1","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n對方真係有興趣，想繼續發展落去的話，真係可以係咁傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都唔覺得大家煩，會仲想繼續傾落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但更多時候，就係遇唔到一個咁樣的人<br />\n所以先諗話題諗到累，諗點樣表達得有趣d 諗到累，諗諗下就唔知點覆，結果又 end左個對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我咪Exact7ly 係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你肯傾，對方都未必有心傾落去<br />\n一句起，兩句止，搵話題都搵到攰</blockquote><br />\n有時係，唔係唔想傾落去，而係唔知點樣再進一步傾落去<br />\n好似想開每一個話題都會變得好唐突咁<br />\n其實好難知對方有冇心傾，又或者連有冇心都講唔上，只係有人搵佢，佢就應下你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己可以做ge野，就只係盡量唔令對方以為自己冇心傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我都係等對方搵我算啦...</blockquote><br />\n如果佢唔搵你，姐係完架嗱bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有搵過，我真係有<br />\n佢覆到勁hea，仲點傾落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 屌 主動拎左電話 主動過 但唔知傾乜鳩好 一問一答咁 佢都好似冇咩意思想問一D關於我既野 我唔搵佢 佢都唔會主動搵我 唉 睇黎都係冇機 我都廢事自己攞柒 A0算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有無機，自己一睇就知<br />\n只係想求有人屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2ab0186861c80e08166a83ab906a4959a5f949","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b125662f21b3714d928c9b4751d38ac4402f8353","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/f