盡量唔令對方以為自己冇心傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我都係等對方搵我算啦...</blockquote><br />\n如果佢唔搵你，姐係完架嗱bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有搵過，我真係有<br />\n佢覆到勁hea，仲點傾落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 屌 主動拎左電話 主動過 但唔知傾乜鳩好 一問一答咁 佢都好似冇咩意思想問一D關於我既野 我唔搵佢 佢都唔會主動搵我 唉 睇黎都係冇機 我都廢事自己攞柒 A0算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有無機，自己一睇就知<br />\n只係想求有人屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問如果 佢都有我電話但佢唔會主動搵我既話 係咪可以收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc843f033d248c065d9940d146a73d06738e73f3","tid":177751,"uid":4727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"好想拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">分手兩星期，冇感覺</span></span>"},{"pid":"c3fac3a98a2e7dd947ae625e824c562b2452d3d7","tid":177751,"uid":19426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">分手兩星期，冇感覺</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你只係想搵個伴 沖淡番之前既情傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac81ec478269955f227261f989947c1c77980249","tid":177751,"uid":4727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好想拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">分手兩星期，冇感覺</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你只係想搵個伴 沖淡番之前既情傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢一齊唔耐，冇乜經歷先冇感覺"}