hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a821ef3c0cd0da4f16c7df6e316550b9da6bf702","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對上一個拍左7年散, 未有錢既情況下, 真係怕左再開始, 一黎驚害左人咁,<br />\n<br />\n有朋友話怕散拖都OK, 但自己係果D一拍就諗住會同人結婚果D黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以兩年無拍了, 雖然有時都想有個人陪下...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意呀<br />\n所以根本就好難再去拍拖，亦都好難遇到啱嘅人"},{"pid":"c76bccdde97def1ae30be53ad66d8b586057847b","tid":177751,"uid":87498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc70bf223a41a1e1dc30a9bc11ecd477b87a68e","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該話人愈大愈冇勇氣去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n尤其之前受過傷，就真係唔想再愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試過熱情去融化佢<br />\n但似乎唔太成功<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又怕自己受傷害"},{"pid":"1b9b2ae34e0ed34b828cd267f5751fbb29fe1a9f","tid":177751,"uid":61324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早呀，巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上返水啦"},{"pid":"7d698182fb9d1bcbf2d90d125b050d19d2d27bb3","tid":177751,"uid":68913,"lik