","tid":177751,"uid":91047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該話人愈大愈冇勇氣去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n尤其之前受過傷，就真係唔想再愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試過熱情去融化佢<br />\n但似乎唔太成功<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又怕自己受傷害</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自問係一個怕受傷既人<br />\n但為左打動佢<br />\n我已經做晒主動去揾佢<br />\n結果都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我希望有一日可以等到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢真係有咁好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608d5962e8f071383ec9f31164d06597d26d411d","tid":177751,"uid":43208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"大家好，碌左入黎<br />\n想同大家傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b155346f52cb9ae40707eb5a556f1578aea8fbf2","tid":177751,"uid":43208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於重新認識一個人感到好厭倦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人大左有惰性<br />\n懶得識人<br />\n唔願試新野"},{"pid":"83960cb33796536021af385d80a6eeb0f239e87e","tid":177751,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意呀<br />\n所以根本就好難再去拍拖，亦都好難遇到啱嘅人</blockquote><br />\n曾經有個女仔比暗示我, 但真係完全無感覺...<br />\n講既野亦唔多岩CHANNEL....<br />\n有女同事話, 點解唔試下先... <br />\n<br />\n我話, 我拍過拖, 知岩既人會有咩感覺, 點解要比假希望人..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417c7d4de673894810ad208ae10c0a42319f25aa","tid":177751,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前係想拍拖而拍拖，只要係正常樣，對你好似好好。都有好感。現在⋯⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n岩呀，女人一開腦就搵有錢仔</blockquote><br />\n有個廿歲頭同事問我, 拍拖要好多錢咩, <br />\n我話係啊, 答你唔係果個, 基本上可能無諗過同你過人世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1814695119e0f540327bba0c036129d7921d776b","tid":177751,"uid":88453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T22:26:06.000Z","msg":"七年未拍過拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  對上果次已經係中學<br />\n而家出到黎社會要識到岩嘅人已經難，莫講話一齊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b76f3f75464ecf645bc1f6a541cd958b122daa","tid":177751,"uid":24529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T22:50:29.000Z","msg":"你揀人都要人揀返你先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1364323daa1d22ee16ed69634fdc6ae3818c3306","tid":177751,"uid":49008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T23:10:23.000Z","msg":"剛失戀留名，個心好似掏空咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f69aadb47fc659a1e4cacdcd83e0c2ee560a16","tid":177751,"uid":93947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該話人愈大愈冇勇氣去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n尤其之前受過傷，就真係唔想再愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試過熱情去融化佢<br />\n但似乎唔太成功<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又怕自己受傷害</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自問係一個怕受傷既人<br />\n但為左打動佢<br />\n我已經做晒主動去揾佢<br />\n結果都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我希望有一日可以等到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢真係有咁好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢唔係完美<br />\n佢自己都話佢唔係我想像中咁好<br />\n但係我眼中，佢係 <br />\n<br />\n人一定無十全十美架啦 <br />\n既然係愛既 就應該接受佢既一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論係佢既優點缺點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔嘗試比我接受佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf0d27d0b5bd15e6837a43cbd27fb9c42635484","tid":177751,"uid":31991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"人大左識人難左<br />\n加上我都幾hurt下<br />\n分左成個月<br />\n有時都覺得手腳冇力, 冇哂心機..."},{"pid":"684b2a080e1c0c2c09679f9385e3006177ea8783","tid":177751,"uid":96123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人大左識人難左<br />\n加上我都幾hurt下<br />\n分左成個月<br />\n有時都覺得手腳冇力, 冇哂心機...</blockquote><br />\n揾啲野做 轉移下視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bd3515faaabb50c5b044d8391313ac8b42c32c","tid":177751,"uid":49008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人大左識人難左<br />\n加上我都幾hurt下<br />\n分左成個月<br />\n有時都覺得手腳冇力, 冇哂心機...</blockquote><br />\n揾啲野做 轉移下視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要分散下注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f161179c76c37d8ba973d1f5e805ffeb471e0dc","tid":177751,"uid":62560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"細個覺得2個人真心真意好易，特別係中學<br />\n出左黎社會遇多左人就發覺自己能力唔夠，好難維持一段關係。<br />\n亦開始遇到堆玩家對手，對感情呢樣野就唔再覺得我對你好，你就會對返我好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /